name: The Veil of The Creators 01
description: The veil of the creator is a digital curatorial response towards the latest Instagram term of use (policy) where it does not provide fair protection for content creators from the possibilities of infringement on content copyrights and privacy. provides minimal pictorial clues to the display work; Like a facade; the visitors have to enter beyond the facade only get to see the works; Or like a banana; where the meat is beyond the skin.
